//! `src_dst_e == boot_endpoint(SYSTEM)` in the SENDREC arm and diverts here
//! instead of calling [`ipc::send::mini_send`]; the rest of the IPC engine is
//! untouched.
//!
//! [`ipc::dispatch`]: crate::ipc
//! [`ipc::send::mini_send`]: crate::ipc

